These pipes appear to be carved of a yellowed dragon bone and tied with a surprisingly tough cord of dragon gut. They creak and wheeze with air, even when not in use.

When played, gouts of flame burst from the ends of the hollows, scorching anyone in their path.

Use this widget to set an item to spawn. It will automatically store the gold cost based on the value of the item being stored. You can override this by setting a local Int variable "cost" to whatever you prefer.

Items created will automatically be marked stolen so they cannot be created and sold, in case the cost set is lower than the value.
